read message window (attachment panel)
  export;  attachment(s) (as filelist)
	   default swing editor stuff (text)
  import:  nothing

new message window
  export:  default swing editor stuff
  import:  other message (file/attachment)
	   file (file/attachment)
 	   key (encrypt/sign)

folder window
  export:  message(s)
  import:  message(s)

folder node
  export:  none
  import:  message(s)

attachment panel
	see read message window.

